data.transfer.tracking

Class FileOperationTracker

  • java.lang.Object
    • data.transfer.tracking.FileOperationTracker
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FileDownloadTracker, FileUploadTracker

    abstract class FileOperationTracker
extends java.lang.Object
    Object responsible of: - Detecting all files that must be transferred to or from the FTP server. - Keep track of file transfer progress and forwards the information using a TrackerProgressCallable object. - Execute the actual file transfers. - Forwards any error that happen along the way.
    Author:
    Thomas Debouverie
